#  Loan Approval Data Analysis

##  Project Overview
This project focuses on analyzing loan application data to understand the factors that influence loan approval decisions.

---

##  Tools & Technologies
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Jupyter Notebook

---

## Dataset Information
The dataset contains information about applicants such as:
- Gender
- Marital Status
- Education
- Self Employed
- Applicant Income
- Coapplicant Income
- Loan Amount
- Loan Amount Term
- Credit History
- Property Area
- Loan Status

---

## Key Steps Performed
- Data Cleaning and Preprocessing  
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)  
- Handling missing values  
- Understanding applicant profiles  
- Identifying approval patterns  

---

## Key Insights
- Credit history plays a major role in loan approval  
- Income level impacts loan eligibility  
- Applicant demographics influence decisions  

---

## Conclusion
This project provided hands-on experience in analyzing financial data and understanding decision-making patterns in loan approvals.

